<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Document</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        .box1 {
            width: 450px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        body {
            background-color: rgba(238, 238, 238);
        }

        ul {
            width: 450px;
            height: 30px;
            list-style: none;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        ul li {
            float: left;
            width: 150px;
            height: 30px;
            line-height: 30px;
            background-color: #000;
            color: #fff;
            text-align: center;
        }

        ul li:hover {
            background-color: #aaa;
        }

        .box {
            height: 300px;
        }

        .news {
            background-color: #fff;
            border-bottom: 1px dotted #aaa;
            padding: 8px 10px;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>

    <div class="box1">
        <nav id="nav">
            <ul>
                <li class="act">热图排行</li>
                <li>美图速递</li>
                <li>前沿科技</li>
            </ul>
        </nav>
        <div class="main" id="main">
            <div class="box">
                <div class="news">习近平出席推进“一带一路”建设工作5周年座谈会</div>
                <div class="news">中共时隔近三年再修党纪条例 这些高压线不能碰</div>
                <div class="news">全国高中2019年秋季起分步实施新课程使用新教材</div>
                <div class="news">个税法修正案草案将二审 起征点会否超5000元？</div>
            </div>
            <div class="box">
                <div class="news">鹅教官、羊陪练... ...这所中学养的动物成了“网红”</div>
                <div class="news">最伤身体的10个生活习惯，一定要避开</div>
                <div class="news">12岁孩子带着父亲去西藏，吃住行自己拿主意</div>
                <div class="news">16岁男孩暑假干了俩月工地，练出满身肌肉，只为赚学费</div>
            </div>
            <div class="box">
                <div class="news">鹅教官、羊陪练... ...啊啊啊啊啊</div>
                <div class="news">最伤身体的10个生活习惯，啦啦啦啦啦</div>
                <div class="news">12岁孩子带着父亲去西藏，哈哈哈哈哈</div>
                <div class="news">16岁男孩暑假干了俩月工地，只为赚学费</div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
<script>
    window.onload = function () {
        var nav = document.getElementById('nav');
        var li = nav.getElementsByTagName('li');
        var main = document.getElementById('main');
        var box = main.getElementsByClassName('box');
        for (var i = 0; i < li.length; i++) {
            li[i].index = i;
            li[i].onmouseenter = function () {
                for (var j = 0; j < li.length; j++) {
                    li[j].className = '';
                    box[j].style.display = "none";
                }
                this.className = 'act';
                box[this.index].style.display = "block";
            }
            for (var t = 1; t < li.length; t++) {
                li[t].className = '';
                box[t].style.display = "none";
            }
        }
    }
</script>

</html>
